       Name: Cloak:mental
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 550
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: @@NThe @@mcloak@@N around your body fades.
Acquisition:
   - Monk: level 48
Description:
   Cloak:mental is the Monk's signature remort cloak. It surrounds the caster
   in a shimmering aura of mental fortitude, providing a flat reduction to all
   incoming non-physical (magical) damage. The reduction amount is equal to
   pseudo_level / 2.

   For example, at pseudo-level 100, every magical hit against the Monk is
   reduced by 50 damage. This reduction is applied before other damage
   modifiers such as elemental resistance.

   The cloak does not affect physical damage. For physical damage reduction,
   see cloak:iron (Knight).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
